## Icons

Remix Icon 4.6.0, loaded in `layout.tsx` via `<link>` in `<head>`. Class pattern: `ri-*-line` or `ri-*-fill`.

Common icons used in this app:
- `ri-phone-fill` / `ri-phone-line` — phone CTA
- `ri-check-line` — checklist items
- `ri-star-fill` — ratings
- `ri-shield-check-line` — trust / accreditation
- `ri-map-pin-2-line` — location
- `ri-award-line` — credentials
- `ri-arrow-right-line` — CTA link arrow
- `ri-heart-line` — personalized care
- `ri-brain-line` — mental health
- `ri-leaf-line` — holistic / nature

**Never use lucide-react or other icon packages** — Remix Icon only.

