## Shared Components (in `src/views/shared/`)

### `PageHero`
Full-width dark hero for all inner pages.

```tsx
import PageHero from "@/views/shared/PageHero";

<PageHero
  eyebrow="Treatment Programs"
  headline="Drug & Alcohol Detox"
  italicWord="Detox"           // wraps first matching word in italic + terracotta
  body="Safe, medically supervised withdrawal..."
  image="https://ahufsygjwpbymomfdazb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/site-assets/images/nbt_XXX.jpg"
  imageAlt="Alt text"
  breadcrumbs={[{ label: "Programs", href: "/programs/" }, { label: "Detox" }]}
/>
```

### `SectionHeader`
Centered or left-aligned eyebrow + h2 + optional body.

```tsx
import SectionHeader from "@/views/shared/SectionHeader";

<SectionHeader
  eyebrow="Our Approach"
  headline="Evidence-Based Treatment"
  italicWord="Treatment"
  body="Optional supporting paragraph..."
  align="center"   // "left" | "center" (default: "left")
  dark={false}     // true = white text (for navy sections)
/>
```

### `CtaBanner`
Navy bottom-of-page CTA strip.

```tsx
import CtaBanner from "@/views/shared/CtaBanner";

<CtaBanner
  headline="Ready to Start Your Recovery?"
  body="Our admissions team is available 24/7."
  primaryCta={{ label: "Verify Insurance", href: "/insurance/" }}
  secondaryCta={{ label: "Call (866) 311-0003", href: "tel:8663110003" }}
/>
```

