## Chrome

All pages (including inner pages) share the same three chrome components:

- `HomeTopBar` — slim top bar with social icons + phone
- `HomeNavigation` — fixed main nav + mega menus
- `HomeFooter` — navy footer

These are wired into `src/components/feature/Layout.tsx` for all non-home, non-admin routes.
Homepage (`/`) renders its own chrome directly in `src/app/page.tsx`.

